    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-12-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-12-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="688" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d688">
                <head>No. 686.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-12-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 26,
                                        1873</date>. (Received Dec. 26,—p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>My resignation having been accepted, I now respectfully renew my
                                request for the publication of the correspondence relating thereto,
                                comprising my telegrams of the 6th, 16th, and 20th instant, and your
                                replies of the 6th, 17th, and 20th. I beg that this request may be
                                submitted to the President.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>SICKLES.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
